channel.title: Help, with zoom port forwarding!
channel.description:
I need help, I have Zoom ADSL X6 modem (same as a router) and there is like, no "Both" icon in protocol section! So will you please give me a small tutorial. The only options are, icmp, igmp, ip, tcp, egp, udp, rsvp, gre, ospf, ipip, and DMZ to choose in the Virtual Server/ DMZ part under protocol.
Cheers, cool dool
